    <item>
      <title>美国 4 月份新增就业岗位 175,000 个，低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-03/us-adds-175-000-jobs-in-april-missing-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国 4 月份新增就业岗位 17.5 万个，为六个月以来最小增幅。预期新增就业岗位 24 万个。失业率小幅上升至 3.9%，工资增长放缓。彭博社的 Michael McKee 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-03/us-adds-175-000-jobs-in-april-missing-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:45:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元升值超过 1%，缓解干预猜测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/yen-strengthens-more-than-1-easing-intervention-speculation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国就业数据未达预期后，日元继续上涨，缓解了有关日本当局可能再次介入市场以支撑陷入困境的货币的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/yen-strengthens-more-than-1-easing-intervention-speculation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:45:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业机会缺失后交易员推迟美联储降息，国债飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/treasury-yields-tumble-as-jobs-data-revives-case-for-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国劳动力市场报告落后于预期后，美国国债飙升，交易员加大了对美联储今年何时开始降息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/treasury-yields-tumble-as-jobs-data-revives-case-for-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:38:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>先锋集团敦促投资者在美联储推迟投资时“调整规模”购买债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/vanguard-urges-investors-right-size-toward-bonds-on-fed-delay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[先锋集团表示，美联储降息步伐的放缓为长期锁定有吸引力的收益率提供了更长的机会，投资者应该“调整”债券而非股票的配置。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/vanguard-urges-investors-right-size-toward-bonds-on-fed-delay</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
