    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Puig 在完成今年欧洲最大的 IPO 后回吐早期涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/rabanne-owner-puig-rises-in-spanish-debut-after-2-6-billion-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙美容和香水集团 Puig Brands SA 及其创始家族在首次公开募股中筹集了 26 亿欧元（合 28 亿美元），该公司的股价在首次公开募股后就回吐了早期涨幅。今年是欧洲最大的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/rabanne-owner-puig-rises-in-spanish-debut-after-2-6-billion-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 10:04:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其通胀率接近 70%，峰值可能即将到来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/turkish-inflation-jumps-again-as-central-bank-hopes-peak-is-near</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其的通货膨胀率已经是世界上最高的国家之一，由于工资上涨等政府政策抵消了激进的加息，土耳其的通货膨胀率连续六个月加速。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/turkish-inflation-jumps-again-as-central-bank-hopes-peak-is-near</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 07:01:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员预计美联储将在 9 月降息，美国国债收益率下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/asian-stocks-to-rise-as-tech-lifts-wall-street-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街将美国就业市场放缓视为美联储最早将于 9 月开始降息的迹象，随着债券收益率大幅走低，交易员推高股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/asian-stocks-to-rise-as-tech-lifts-wall-street-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 22:31:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
