      <title>市场寻找日元干预美联储账户的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/market-hunts-for-signs-of-japan-yen-intervention-in-fed-accounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储各种账户的最新数据暗示，日本政策制定者可能会通过两种潜在方式为过去一周的货币干预行动提供资金，以提振日元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/market-hunts-for-signs-of-japan-yen-intervention-in-fed-accounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 21:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
